hopobject.body: I'm a member of a gym deluxe leather lifting straps Just as they hoped, Jessica, now 16, has grown up in an idyllic setting, with freedom she may never have had if they’d stayed in the city. True to the Famous Five stories, she has spent every summer with her four first cousins, exploring the coves, caves and beaches, picnicking, rock pooling, canoeing in the gentle waters and feeding the farm animals. Despite the demands of running the holiday lets, her parents have enjoyed the beautiful cliff walks, opportunities for sailing, and hosting gatherings on the farm. “It has become a whole-family adventure,” Elizabeth says. “When Jeremy’s brothers and sisters come for huge gatherings at school holidays, the children go off to the beach, and the adults pitch in with the running of the business. We’ve been able to hand them the reins so we can have a break.”
